title: 이달의소녀탐구 #95 (LOONA TV #95)
summary:
The girls are in a soccer field.
0:05 -- HyunJin: “I am good at soccer… But I can’t do now. Because I’m wearing heels.”
0:14 -- HyunJin kicks the ball (and kicks it really good!)
0:21 -- “If I was wearing sneakers, I could beat them all!!”
It’s Basketball Time!
0:28 -- HyunJin shows her basketball game. She never misses a shot.
0:36 -- HeeJin: “She was a member of the school soccer club, table tennis club,
basketball club. Even a tennis or a badminton club. She is very strong~!"
